=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做乜咁儍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我幫過射撚滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18cf1901631b71ef408bdd3240e665d447c51ec0","tid":250783,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"文匯有報.."},{"pid":"435e98165f7309d67f734baac919d9ca5ce80686","tid":250783,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:33:27.000Z","msg":"連港獨都被熱狗，班外人又點會知熱普城內部做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1456e5c693a238a6228a149c4f349588a769244","tid":250783,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"網台私怨上報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39649cebbf11261a4e1241fc48da4932bc2476d0","tid":250783,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/194454_7e77733dce97cf329d52813489d79fab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F194454_7e77733dce97cf329d52813489d79fab.jpg&h=d7219c26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8281796eb6f1db06298aabd5d503168b0dca091d","tid":250783,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"咁上次毒果報左佢寂滅<br />\n10個月後都未寂滅<br />\n今次仲咁得閒理佢咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">隔牆有耳：告別　專欄　網台　facebook<br />\n敗選國師　預告寂滅</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20160908/large/a1603a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160908%2Flarge%2Fa1603a.gif&h=53a6657a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺新界東落選嘅香港復興會陳云根、即係國師陳雲，喺facebook貼文，首句「各位陳雲haters，我告退了」，震驚唔少國民。國師話喎，會喺合約結束後，終止現時僅有嘅兩個網媒專欄，即係雅虎網站、熱血時報，同時亦會終止MyRadio嘅《本土論壇》。<br />\n唔見聲唔見文都未止，佢話適當時候會停用𠵱家嘅facebook賬戶：「網上的我將會逐步消失，直至寂滅，包括這個我用了多年的面書戶口，將在適當時候終止。」<br />\n到底發生咗乜事？睇睇佢喺投票後，講過乜嘢先！其實喺新東攞到二萬三千幾票、敗選但查實得票唔差嘅國師，喺facebook話過「香港人不配擁有國家」，並指：「陳雲逆天而行，妄圖為香港人無痛地建立香港國來度過厄難，今後閉門思過，不再見無謂之客，不淨之人。」<br />\n佢當時仲提及雷動計劃，「我的港獨計劃，用永續基本法的憲政技術，部署一年，先後徵得美國贊同、中共不反對，然而被香港人否決了，很多投票者信任泛民的雷動計劃而一票不給陳雲，在最後幾個小時等待戴耀廷的指示，蜂擁往票站配票，令陳雲功敗垂成」，似乎都好不滿喎。<br />\n<br />\n「往後只見喜歡的人」<br />\n咁以後仲有冇機會見到國師？國師明言：「往後，只有我喜歡的人，才會在現場見到我。」唔知一直喺國師facebook得到心靈慰藉嘅粉絲，係咪從此傷心鳥？"},{"pid":"624585f1a24b4d3ade1742c9cd74ba6f1bec4461","tid":250783,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/194454_7e77733dce97cf329d52813489d79fab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F194454_7e77733dce97cf329d52813489d79fab.jpg&h=d7219c26&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻根<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427f10906aac913c1480fd1b7e21a71e6c5db75b","tid":250783,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"點解要報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f89ee48c5808e5